OL,3,CFire rips through children's nursery
OL,4,Cin Berkshire overnight
OL,6,FA fire has torn through a children's
OL,7,Fnursery in Thatcham overnight forcing
OL,8,Fthe school to close as staff assess
OL,9,Fthe situation.
OL,11,FLocal residents said they saw a fire
OL,12,Fraging at the nursery in the early
OL,13,Fhours.
OL,15,FThe shell of a building could be seen
OL,16,Fthis morning at the site. It's unclear
OL,17,Fwhether anyone was in the building at
OL,18,Fthe time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
