OL,3,CFire rips through children's nursery
OL,4,Cin Berkshire overnight
OL,6,FFire crews were called to the site at
OL,7,F1.30am this morning (10 March) to
OL,8,Freports of a fire at a nursery on
OL,9,FTurnpike Road.
OL,11,FCrews from Newbury, Theale,
OL,12,FHungerford, Mortimer and Whitley Wood
OL,13,Fwere sent to the scene, together with
OL,14,Fa crew from Hampshire and Isle of
OL,15,FWight Fire and Rescue Service.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the nursery said it
OL,18,Fwill be in touch with families as soon
OL,19,Fas it has an update.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
