OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773155489
OL,3,CFire rips through children's nursery
OL,4,Cin Berkshire overnight
OL,6,FThey said: "As many of you have seen
OL,7,Fon social media there has been a fire
OL,8,Fat Tigers in Thatcham.
OL,10,F"The nursery will closed today and we
OL,11,Fwill assess the situation. We will be
OL,12,Fin touch with our families as soon as
OL,13,Fwe have news. "
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Royal Berkshire
OL,16,FFire and Rescue Service said: "Upon
OL,17,Farrival firefighters found two
OL,18,Fbuildings involved in the fire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
