CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1773155489
OL,3,CFire rips through children's nursery
OL,4,Cin Berkshire overnight
OL,6,F"Crews extinguished the fire using two
OL,7,Fmain jets, two hose reels and the
OL,8,Faerial ladder platform.
OL,10,F"No casualties have been reported at
OL,11,Fthis incident.
OL,13,F"The fire is now under control,
OL,14,Fhowever, crews remain at the scene
OL,15,Fdamping down to ensure the fire is
OL,16,Ffully extinguished.
OL,18,F"This premise is likely to remain
OL,19,Fclosed at this time."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
